        <title>ACTIVITY 1: Number Patterns (Mental calculations) [LO 2.2] </title>
        <list id="id4602490" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Let us see how you cope with the following mental calculations. Try and complete the test in less than two minutes.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id4599266">a) 12 × 8 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4533363">b) 23 + 38 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4600556">c) 48 + _________________ = 61</para>
        <para id="id4600317">d) 132 ÷ _________________ = 11</para>
        <para id="id4599669">e) 71 – 18 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4602437">f) _________________ ÷ 6 = 9</para>
        <para id="id4602388">g) 63 + 19 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4602213">h) 39 + . _________________ = 63</para>
        <para id="id4602164">i) 7 × _________________ = 560</para>
        <para id="id4601807">j) Double 89: _________________</para>
        <para id="id4601686">k) 90 × 30 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4601512">l) R4,50 × 20 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4601471">m) 400 × 60 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4601296">n) 2 700 ÷ . _________________ = 30</para>
        <para id="id4600515">o) R6,08 × 10 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4600236">p) R2,37 × 100 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4599796">q) 3/8 of 64 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4600194">r) 4/5 of 45 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4602189">s) 6/7 of 42 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id4602067">t) Halve 68,5: _________________</para>
        <para id="id4601268">I have . ________________________________________. correct.</para>
        <list id="id4601212" list-type="bulleted">
