        <para id="id4600668"><emphasis effect="bold">8</emphasis>. Look at the interesting pattern we can find on a calendar.</para>
        <list id="id4600698" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Work with a friend and discuss:</item>
        </list>
        <figure id="id4600289">
          <media id="id4600289_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics4-9878.png" id="id4600289__onlineimage" height="134" width="275"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
        <para id="id4600065">a) What pattern can you see in each row? (horizontal)</para>
        <para id="id4600095">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4600100">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4600014">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4600020">b) What pattern can be seen in each column? (vertical)</para>
        <para id="id4599943">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599949">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599953">c) What patterns do you see in the diagonal from left to right?</para>
        <para id="id4599897">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599916">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599922">d) What patterns do you see in the diagonal from right to left?</para>
        <para id="id4599812">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599818">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599743">e) Look at the block marked with a dark line on the calendar. Now determine:</para>
        <para id="id4599620">f) The sum of each row: ________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4599412">g) The sum of each column: _____________________________________________</para>
        <list id="id4510266" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>What do you notice? _______________________________________________________________</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id4498619">h) The sum of the diagonals: ____________________________________________</para>
        <list id="id4526740" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>What do you notice? _______________________________________________________________</item>
        </list>
